             âf. f â fc â§ {i | i â J â§ satis (Ms i) (f i) phi\} â U)}

Given a world in \HOLtm{(ultraproduct_model U J Ms)}, we prove \HOLtm{satis (ultraproduct_model U J Ms) fc (â phi) â
